room_title: Escape room "Time Machine" by Puzzled Escape Rooms in Fargo
room_address: 114 Broadway N Suite L1 Fargo, ND 58102
room_description: Our own Professor Chronos Zeitenspiel has succeeded in inventing a time machine. You were invited to a demonstration of the device but unfortunately something has gone wrong and the Professor is lost in time. Can you help the Professor return to our time before the machine's battery runs out in an hour?
